'''Ryn City''', also known as '''Section 465''', was the area of [[Ruan]]'s [[Refugee Facility 17]] that contained its thirty-seven [[Ryn/Legends|Ryn]]. It was located behind the facility's communal [[Refresher/Legends|refresher]], and its leader was [[R'vanna]].

